# `package.json` `files` is the authoritative inclusion list
# (`dist/*.js`, `dist/*.d.ts`, `dist/catalog.json`). This file is
# defense-in-depth — same exclusions in case `files` is ever
# broadened to `["dist"]`.

# Build-time scripts — not consumed at runtime by `npx auriga-cli`.
# Their only job is to emit dist/catalog.json during `npm run build`.
dist/build/

# Test artifacts (compiled tests live under dist-test/, not dist/, but
# excluded here defensively in case that ever changes).
dist-test/
tests/
